after death is a 1988 italian zombie film . the film is set on a remote island where a voodoo curse that raises the dead from their graves to feast on the flesh of the living . when a boat containing a group of explorers which includes a young girl who experienced the zombie uprising years earlier , makes an emergency &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; on the island , the crew find that their only hope for survival is a protective idol given to the young girl by her mother years ago .